ComicInfo.Summary: For the last nine months, Katchoo has been working hard to keep her mind off Francine's wedding by painting . . . nude pictures of Sara?! Poor Sara never knew what she was getting into when the FBI assigned her to go undercover and keep an eye on Katchoo. Now, everybody's eyes are on her as 100 nude paintings of her voluptuous body debut at Katchoo's first major art exhibit.
